stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_load_el: load EL blobSchedule entries
    q_load_el --> q_load_cl: load CL BLOB_SCHEDULE entries
    q_load_cl --> q_iter: for each BPO fork
    q_iter --> q_check_slot: validate EL slot aligns with CL epoch start
    q_check_slot --> q_fail_slot: EL slot != start_of_epoch(CL epoch)
    q_check_slot --> q_check_max: EL slot == start_of_epoch(CL epoch)
    q_fail_slot --> [*]: revert inconsistent slot/epoch alignment
    q_check_max --> q_fail_max: EL max != CL MAX_BLOBS_PER_BLOCK
    q_check_max --> q_pass: EL max == CL MAX_BLOBS_PER_BLOCK
    q_fail_max --> [*]: revert inconsistent max blob count
    q_pass --> q_iter: validate next fork
    q_iter --> [*]: all forks validated successfully
